newsitem.title: USA: U.S. soyoil weekly export sales highlights - USDA.
newsitem.headline: U.S. soyoil weekly export sales highlights - USDA.

text.p: USDA soyoil weekly export sales highlights in latest reporting week:
Soybean Oil: Sales of 42,700 MT were primarily the result of increases for unknown destinations (25,000 MT), China (10,000 MT), and Mexico (3,100 MT).
Exports of 3,400 MT were to Mexico (3,200 MT) and Canada (200 MT).
